trans-unit.source: Provides a regular expression to parse the opening tag of an HTML element, an XML element, or an ASP.NET Web server control tag.
trans-unit.target: 提供規則運算式，以剖析 HTML 項目、XML 項目或 ASP.NET Web 伺服器控制項標記中的開頭標記。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.RegularExpressions.TagRegex> class provides a regular expression that ASP.NET uses internally to parse the opening tag of an HTML element, an XML element, or an ASP.NET Web server control tag, for applications that target the [!INCLUDE[net_v40_long](~/includes/net-v40-long-md.md)] or later versions.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.RegularExpressions.TagRegex>類別會提供規則運算式，ASP.NET 會在內部用來剖析 HTML 項目、 XML 項目或 ASP.NET Web 伺服器控制項標記，目標的應用程式的開頭標記[!INCLUDE[net_v40_long](~/includes/net-v40-long-md.md)]或更新版本。

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET uses the <xref:System.Web.RegularExpressions.TagRegex35?displayProperty=nameWithType> class for applications that target the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_short](~/includes/net-v35-short-md.md)] and earlier versions.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET 會使用<xref:System.Web.RegularExpressions.TagRegex35?displayProperty=nameWithType>應用程式類別為目標[!INCLUDE[net_v35_short](~/includes/net-v35-short-md.md)]及較早版本。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.RegularExpressions> classes are used internally by the .NET Framework to parse ASP.NET pages.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.RegularExpressions>類別用於在內部.NET Framework 所剖析的 ASP.NET 網頁。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.RegularExpressions.TagRegex" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.RegularExpressions.TagRegex" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.RegularExpressions.TagRegex" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.RegularExpressions.TagRegex" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: A time-out interval, or <see cref="F:System.Text.RegularExpressions.Regex.InfiniteMatchTimeout" /> if matching operations should not time out.
trans-unit.target: 逾時間隔，如果比對作業不應該逾時，則為 <see cref="F:System.Text.RegularExpressions.Regex.InfiniteMatchTimeout" />。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.RegularExpressions.TagRegex" /> class with a specified time-out value.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的逾時值，初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.RegularExpressions.TagRegex" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The `A_1` parameter represents the maximum time interval during which the regular expression engine tries to find a match before the operation times out and a <xref:System.Text.RegularExpressions.RegexMatchTimeoutException> expression is thrown.
trans-unit.target: `A_1`參數表示的最大時間間隔期間的規則運算式引擎會嘗試尋找相符項目，作業逾時之前，<xref:System.Text.RegularExpressions.RegexMatchTimeoutException>運算式就會擲回。
